<p><font face="helvetica"><b>Description:</b></font></p>
<p>Bouncy is a simple application which can display an image file that you drag and drop onto it, even a transparent image, and bounce it across your desktop.  The program simulates gravity and will &#147;bounce&#148; of the bottom and sides of the screen.</p>
<p></p>
<p><font face="helvetica"><b>Topics:</b></font></p>
<p>The key topics covered in this Project are:</p>
<p>   - How to create an irregularly shaped window</p>
<p>   - How to handle a file being drag dropped onto a window</p>
<p>   - How to move a window by script</p>
<p>   - How to simulate gravity and play sounds on collision with the edge of the screen</p>